  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Cost: 4-6 Creation Points </p><p></p><p>You throw a B.I.M designed to weaken creatures enough that they surrender, or that dispatching them becomes a trivial task.</p><p> Each creature within 15 feet of the target space must make a Constitution saving throw.</p><p> On a failed save, a creature takes 4d4 bludgeoning damage and gains 1 rank of Bruised or half as much damage and no additional effects on a successful one.</p><p> Upgraded: For every 1 Creation Point after the minimum initial cost increase the damage dice by 1 or the ranks of Bruised by 1</p>",
